{
  "stem": "24259.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm told that at times, being a young child, and for some reason I would be uncomfortable, and I would cry, my mother would have to kind of muffle my sound to a point where she would almost choke me.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm also told that I learned to cry mimicking the sounds of a cat or a dog animal so that we wouldn't be discovered.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I also remember my mother telling me stories about how things will be when we were liberated later on, kind of just to keep me amused, if you will.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She would talk about having, you know, good food, and being able to cook again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we would be living in a house again in the-- in the-- in the daylight.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those are some of the things that she used to talk about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Those were big things in those days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't recall anyone specifically being sick.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know my mother, I guess, had from the dampness rheumatism arthritis.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that would bother her a great deal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at one time, when we had to escape out of the hole because the barn was set afire, she was so badly inflicted that she wasn't able to lift herself out of the hole.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she actually stayed there with my-- my aunt after my father and I escaped out of the hole.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At the-- at the first farm that we stayed in in the hole, we stayed there for maybe eight or nine months.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the barn was set afire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my-- my mother finally persuaded my father to-- she was having difficulty getting out-- to take me and-- and run out of the barn.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father grabbed me and ran out into the wheat fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
